summary: Blue Roses Ch. 9 - Friendship, the Bond that Helps you Trick your Friends!
title: Blue Roses Ch. 9 - Friendship, the Bond that Helps you Trick your Friends!
body:
Chapter 9 Word Count: 3262

Chapter 9 Summary:  TJ, more determined now than ever, recruits Jonah to help him find out who his ‘unknown enigma’ is. Unbeknownst to either of them, Cyrus enlists the help of Buffy to keep his identity a secret for even longer.

New Chapters Every Sunday and Wednesday!


           After school, Cyrus headed straight to Judy’s Blooms to pick up his flowers with a new note from TJ weighing heavily in his pocket. It felt like the note was calling out for him to open it while he waited for the clerk to bring the flowers out; he just couldn’t stop thinking about it, but he knew that the flower shop was not the place to read it. When the clerk finally reappeared with the flowers, Cyrus paid for them as quickly as possible and headed home, hoping that he wouldn’t see anyone that he knew… or anyone that would ask him either a) who the flowers were for, or b) why he, a middle school boy, had so many flowers.

           It seemed that luck was on Cyrus’ side (for once), and he made it home without being seen by anyone who would wonder what he was doing. He quickly put the flowers where they needed to go before heading up to his room where he could finally read TJ’s note in peace.

Read the Rest on Ao3!

I hope you all enjoy this new chapter! Please reblog to share if you want!

blog.description: Of course I came

body:
50 days of Andi Mack

Season 2 Episode 3: Friends Like These

  • Amber was just trying to be nice but Andi had to be all passive aggressive about it
  • “Why would she ever want to be friends with me?” “Maybe she likes you” If I was an Ambi shipper I would totally be freaking out about that
  • “Would you like to Van Gough to my house tomorrow night?” “I’d louvre to!” More cringy Ciris puns
  • “I can’t get over us, we’re perfect for each other” Well Iris, about that…
  • OMIGOD IT’S TJ MY BOOOOI
  • I forgot how much of a stereotypical bully TJ was to begin with
  • “TJ hates me” “I hate TJ. Who’s TJ?” Little does he know…
  • Since when was “My dogs are barking” waitress speech for “My feet hurt?”
  • Andi just copying everything Buffy says to pretend she has wisdom to impress Bex
  • I hate seeing Marty sad noooo
  • The ghc spying on Amber… Ok then
  • “As a herpetologist I know that that’s not accurate reptile behaviour, but as a lover of stories, A+” Did I ever mention that I love Cyrus Goodman?
  • Was that kiss Cyrus gave Iris actually a goodbye kiss?
  • “What a waste. I can’t believe some potato gave its life for this”
  • “You can’t bring up a topic and then not talk about it” Try telling that to my friends
  • That “Buffy am I going to be ok?” really got me
  • Andi and Amber talking behind Jonah’s back reminds me of Andi and Libby doing the same. Jonah just can’t get a break
  • It was very brave of Bex to put Gabriel into the box
  • That old picture of Bex and Bowie is so adorable

summary: Oh my god can you give some trans!TJ headcanons I thought I was the only one who liked it-
question: Oh my god can you give some trans!TJ headcanons I thought I was the only one who liked it-
answer:
- Acts very hyper-masculine because Fear™ but is starting to unlearn his toxic behaviours and now knows that a gentler approach to life is okay and doesn’t make his identity any less valid

- A Gym Bro For Sure.

- “Feel my muscles!” “TJ you’ve only been on T for two weeks-” “SHUT UP AND FEEL THEM!”

- Bit of a weenie when it comes to needles so it always takes him ten years to actually do his shot

- Asked Andi to teach him to sew and make clothes because he couldn’t afford to buy a new binder so he made his own (very carefully and following legit safe instructions

- Gets excited when he noticed one (1) hair on his face that he’s sure wasn’t there before

- Was pretty good at making his voice deeper before he was on T but when he goes on it no one is prepared for Just How Deep his voice gets
